attributes.title: Yikes.

attributes.review: Sub-par app for a sub-par president. Riddled with grammatical and mechanical errors. Makes me sad that he’s trying to divide the country even further when what we need more than ever is for someone to bring us together again. I am an American patriot in that I want to create a world where my friends feel welcome in their own country instead of being ashamed of and embarrassed by the person who runs it.
